title: Scrapland.XBOX-WAM
description:
SCRAPLAND is a third person action-adventure game set in a
  stunningly beautiful and futuristic world occupied by an 
  amazing array of robotic characters. The play experience is
  driven by a solidly engaging, sometimes humorous adventure
  narrative. The game mechanic combines proven GTA3 style
  emergent action with an immersive storyline, diversity of
  player actions, and complete freedom of movement through 
  the world.
